summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2010 RAM 1500. THE CONTACT STATED THAT WITH THE KEY IN THE IGNITION SWITCH, THE VEHICLE FAILED TO START. AFTER MOVING THE KEY AROUND IN THE IGNITION FOR A WHILE THE VEHICLE STARTED.  THE VEHICLE WAS NOT TAKEN TO THE DEALER NOR AN INDEPENDENT MECHANIC TO BE DIAGNOSED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE. THE APPROXIMATE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 52,900.
